## Saturday Session

# Run Warmup [Running]

- warmup 10min @Z1
- 4x:
  - run 1min @Z4
  - recover 1min @Z1
- rest 2min

# Chipper [HIIT]

- for-time 25min:
  - run 400m
  - Kettlebell Swing 21rep @24kg
  - Pull-Up 15rep
  - run 400m
  - Kettlebell Swing 15rep @24kg
  - Pull-Up 12rep
  - run 400m
  - Kettlebell Swing 9rep @24kg
  - Pull-Up 9rep

- rest 3min

# Cooldown [Running]

- cooldown 5min @Z1
- walk 5min @Z1

> Focus on deep breathing and bringing HR below 120bpm.
